Then with glad Hearts submissively they bring The choicest Spoils with Homage to the King : While those whose Business is to till the Ground , With whom a Sword or Spear is seldom found , Manure their Land , their fruitful Vineyards dress ; They reap their Corn , and luscious Clusters press : And when the Harvest does their Toil reward , They bring their Tribute to their Sovereign Lord
Clemency within his Breast take Place , His People all
he lays him down to sleep , While armed Bands strict Watch do round him keep
Whom in such Sort all Men on Earth obey

appears in place , A royal Youth of David's kingly Race , ( Much nobler he than those that spoke before , Because he did the living GOD adore ) And thus his Mind and Writing did declare Before them all , that fate in Judgement there , Most worthy Princes
Her Beauty to adore they are inclined , Her noble Virtue

In Toil and Labour hard he spends the Day , To gather Wealth , that so he may provide Treasure to bring unto his dearest Bride : Another boldly , with a Sword in Hand , Will cross the Seas , and wander on the Land
if his native Country lay at Stake
Unto his Wife alone his Heart does cleave : Nought
A beauteous Female cruel and unkind
All stand in fear of him ; his Power is such , It's Death to strike , no less than Death to touch
The Honours due to sovereign Majesty
no less than Death to touch

While Men on Earth with trembling Fear implore Almighty Truth , which ever shall endure , When worldly Pomp and Splendour are no more

from Truth to act unfaithfully : Fraud or Deceit in Truth we never find ; Good Men embrace it with a ready Mind : Whatever Thing is virtuous , good , and great , In Truth we find it perfect and complete : Then praised be Truth to all Eternity , In whom alone is Strength and Majesty

With thankful Heart , and joyful Lips , did raise His Voice to sing his great Creator's Praise
